# CODEOWNERS — authority boundary for the external benchmark firewall
#
# Any PR that modifies the files below requires review approval from the
# listed owner before it can merge. Combined with branch protection on
# main (required review + required status checks), this enforces
# separation of authority between author and reviewer for the benchmark
# schema contract.
#
# Rationale: SCHEMA_MAP.md and its version registry define the anti-leakage
# contract for the NYC external benchmark. Silent edits to either file
# invalidate all prior benchmark results. The test_schema_map_sha_matches_version
# check catches unintentional drift; CODEOWNERS catches the intentional case
# by forcing a reviewer in the loop.

benchmarks/SCHEMA_MAP.md             @MarwaBS
benchmarks/SCHEMA_MAP_VERSIONS.json  @MarwaBS
benchmarks/invariants.py             @MarwaBS
